    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:198'>欽定四庫全書　　　　　經部三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='198:214'>　三家詩拾遺　　　　　　詩類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='214:220'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:240'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案三家詩拾遺十卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='240:263'>　　　國朝范家相撰家相字蘅洲㑹稽人乾隆甲戌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='263:286'>　　　　進士官至柳州府知府漢代傳詩者四家隋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='286:309'>　　　　書經籍志稱齊詩亡于魏魯詩亡于西晉惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='309:332'>　　　　韓詩存宋修太平御覽多引韓詩崇文總目</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='332:358'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='358:381'>　　　　亦著錄劉安世晁説之尚時時述其遺説而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='381:404'>　　　　南渡儒者不復論及知亡于政和建炎間矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='404:427'>　　　　自鄭樵以後人人務立新義以掊擊漢儒為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='427:450'>　　　　能雖毛傳鄭箋亦岌岌乎不能自立特以刋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='450:473'>　　　　板太學僅得幸存三家之佚文遂散失而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='473:496'>　　　　可復問王應麟於咸淳之末始掇拾殘賸輯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='496:519'>　　　　為詩攷三卷然剙始難工多所挂漏又增綴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='519:542'>　　　　逸詩篇目襍採諸子依託之説亦頗少持擇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='542:568'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='568:592'>　　　　　家相是編因王氏之書重加裒輯增入者十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='592:616'>　　　　　之六七其以三百篇為綱而三家佚説一一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='616:640'>　　　　　併見較王氏所錄以三家各自為篇者亦頗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='640:664'>　　　　　易循覽惟其以三家詩拾遺為名則古文考</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='664:688'>　　　　　異不盡三家之文者自宜附錄其逸詩不繫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='688:712'>　　　　　于三家者亦自宜芟除乃一例收入未免失</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='712:736'>　　　　　于貪多且冠于篇端使開卷即名實相乖尤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='736:760'>　　　　　非體例至於張超稱關雎為畢公作一條語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='760:786'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='786:809'>　　　　本見超所作誚青衣賦非超别有解經之書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='809:832'>　　　　而但據詩補傳所載泛稱張超云云並不錄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='832:855'>　　　　其賦語蒐采亦間有未周然較王氏之書則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='855:878'>　　　　詳贍逺矣近時嚴虞惇作詩經質疑内有三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='878:901'>　　　　家遺説一篇又惠棟九經古義余蕭客古經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='901:924'>　　　　解鈎沈于三家均有採掇論其賅備亦尚不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='924:945'>　　　　及是編也乾隆四十四年四月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='945:977'>　　　　　　　總纂宫<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='977:1003'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1003:1029'>　　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸　費　墀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1049:1075'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-4a' );" name="000-4a" class="pb">[000-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1075:1084'>三家詩拾遺原序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1084:1107'>魯齊燕韓詩在漢最爲早出後爲毛公所掩遂至亡佚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1107:1130'>歴唐宋至今未有舉其遺説而述之者嘗疑三家師承</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1130:1153'>至遠其弟子如孔安國匡衡王吉諸人皆當世名儒申</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1153:1176'>公之師浮邱伯與毛本出一家何至相懸如是因集三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1176:1199'>家之說散見於經傳子史之引用者反覆推覽多與禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1199:1222'>記周官左國不合而毛獨條條可復此毛之所以得掩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1222:1245'>前人者然三家之說令人欣然頥解者固觸目皆是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1245:1271'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-4b' );" name="000-4b" class="pb">[000-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1271:1294'>經師專己守殘昌黎深嫉其弊今之學者視漢唐注疏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1294:1317'>若可覆瓿不知注疏未可廢也義理求而日出古註亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1317:1340'>探而彌新漢唐縱有缺敗其可傳者自在豈可任其散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1340:1363'>佚而不爲之収拾哉嗟乎詩自朱傳一出即毛傳尚束</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1363:1386'>之高閣何論三家然集傳每取匡劉韓子之説以糾毛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1386:1409'>傳之失矣非其説之原有可信者在歟今使三家之書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1409:1432'>與毛俱存則朱子之駁三家者當甚於毛唯僅存一二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1432:1455'>見其有禆於經而採之彌覺其可重然則三家之說之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1455:1481'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-5a' );" name="000-5a" class="pb">[000-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1481:1504'>是者固當信從其非者亦不妨任其兩存也余因毛鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1504:1527'>箋傳之不行於世而有感於三家之亡於是就深寧王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1527:1550'>氏之詩攷更爲蒐補稍爲推論其得失附以古文考異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1550:1573'>及逸詩二卷名之曰拾遺將以問諸好古之士乾隆庚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1573:1590'>辰四月長至後十日㑹稽范家相自序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1613:1639'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-6a' );" name="000-6a" class="pb">[000-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1639:1646'>三家詩源流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1646:1654'>　　三家總記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1654:1677'>漢書曰漢興魯申公爲詩訓故而齊轅固生燕韓生皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1677:1700'>爲之傳或取春秋采雜説咸非其本義與不得已魯最</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1700:1705'>爲近之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1705:1725'>應劭曰申公作魯詩后蒼作齊詩韓嬰作韓詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1725:1748'>隋經籍志曰漢初魯人申公受詩於浮邱伯作訓詁是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1748:1771'>爲魯詩轅固生亦傳詩是爲齊詩燕人韓嬰亦傳詩是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1771:1797'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-6b' );" name="000-6b" class="pb">[000-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1797:1820'>爲韓詩終於後漢三家並立齊詩魏代已亡魯詩亡於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1820:1832'>西晉韓詩雖存無傳之者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1832:1855'>　按韓詩内傳太平御覽尚引其文劉安世以爲少時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1855:1878'>　嘗讀韓詩是内傳之亡當在北宋之末所存者外傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1878:1885'>　一卷而已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1885:1893'>　　魯詩傳授</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1893:1916'>漢書曰楚元王交字游高祖同父少弟也少時嘗與魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1916:1939'>穆生白生申生俱受詩於浮邱伯伯者孫卿門人也高</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1939:1965'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-7a' );" name="000-7a" class="pb">[000-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1965:1988'>后時浮邱伯在長安元王遣子郢客與申公俱卒業元</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1988:2011'>王好詩諸子皆讀詩申公始爲詩傳號魯詩元王亦次</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2011:2021'>之詩傳號元王詩傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2021:2044'>漢書申公魯人少從楚元王俱事齊人浮邱伯受詩漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2044:2067'>興高祖過魯申公以弟子從師入見於魯南宮武帝使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2067:2090'>使束帛加璧安車以蒲裹輪駕駟迎申公至時已八十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2090:2113'>餘以爲太中大夫病免歸數年卒弟子爲博士十餘人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2113:2136'>孔安國周霸夏寛碭魯賜蘭陵繆生徐偃鄒人闕門慶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2136:2162'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-7b' );" name="000-7b" class="pb">[000-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2162:2185'>忌申公卒以詩春秋授而瑕邱江公盡能傳之及魯許</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2185:2209'>生免中徐公皆守學敎授韋賢治詩至丞相子𤣥成以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2209:2232'>淮陽中尉論石渠後亦至丞相由是魯詩有韋氏學王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2232:2255'>式翁思事免中徐公及許生爲昌邑王師山陽張長安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2255:2279'>幼君先事式後東平唐長賓沛禇少孫亦來事式皆爲博</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2279:2303'>士由是魯詩有張唐禇氏之學張生兄子㳺卿爲諫議大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2303:2330'>夫其門人瑯琊王扶陳留許晏由是張家有許氏學<span class='krp-note'>按/魯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2330:2363'><span class='krp-note'>詩與韋賢同時者有章氏學後漢武/榮治韋氏章句有武氏學不可悉載</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2363:2389'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-8a' );" name="000-8a" class="pb">[000-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2389:2412'>陸德明曰申公以詩經爲訓故以敎無傳疑者則闕弗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2412:2439'>傳<span class='krp-note'>儒林/傳</span>號曰魯詩弟子爲博士者十餘人郎中王臧御</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2439:2462'>史大夫趙綰臨淮太守孔安國膠西内史周霸城陽内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2462:2485'>史夏寛東海太守魯賜長沙内史繆生膠西中尉徐偃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2485:2500'>膠東内史闕門慶忌皆申公弟子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2500:2518'>漢藝文志魯說二十八卷魯故二十五卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2518:2526'>　　齊詩傳授</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2526:2549'>漢書轅固齊人以治詩孝景時爲博士諸齊以詩貴顯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2549:2575'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-8b' );" name="000-8b" class="pb">[000-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2575:2598'>者皆固之弟子也夏侯始昌最明傳后蒼蒼字近君東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2598:2621'>海郯人通詩禮爲博士至少府授翼奉蕭望之匡衡衡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2621:2644'>授瑯琊師丹㐲理斿君潁川滿昌君都由是齊詩有翼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2644:2651'>匡師㐲之學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2651:2674'>陸德明曰轅固生作詩傳號齊詩傳夏侯始昌授后蒼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2674:2697'>蒼授翼奉及蕭望之匡衡衡授師丹及伏理滿昌昌授</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2697:2720'>張邯及皮容皆至大官徒衆尤盛後漢陳元方亦傳齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2720:2723'>詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2723:2749'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-9a' );" name="000-9a" class="pb">[000-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2749:2781'>漢藝文志齊詩傳二十九卷<span class='krp-note'>苟悅漢紀云轅固/生作詩内外傳</span>后氏蒼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2781:2804'>齊故二十卷傳三十九卷孫氏故二十七卷傳二十八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2804:2812'>卷雜記十八卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2812:2820'>　　韓詩傳授</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2820:2843'>漢書曰韓嬰燕人推詩人之意而作内外傳數萬言其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2843:2866'>語頗與齊魯間殊然歸一也淮南賁生受之燕趙間言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2866:2889'>詩者由韓生河南趙子事生授同郡蔡誼誼授同郡食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2889:2912'>子公與王吉食生授泰山栗豐豐授山陽張就吉授淄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2912:2938'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-9b' );" name="000-9b" class="pb">[000-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2938:2959'>川長孫順順授東海髮福由是有王食長孫之學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2959:2992'>漢藝文志韓故三十六卷<span class='krp-note'>新唐書韓詩卜商序/韓嬰注二十二卷</span>内傳四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2992:3013'>卷外傳六卷<span class='krp-note'>隋唐志/十卷</span>詩說四十一卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3013:3026'>　　漢魏說詩不著傳授者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3026:3049'>伏生尚書大傳時或引詩伏本魯人與申公先後同時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3049:3063'>是魯詩家伏湛治魯詩見本傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3063:3086'>淮南子鴻烈解集衆手成書其說詩不一然家世魯詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3086:3093'>也亦爲魯詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3093:3120'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-10a' );" name="000-10a" class="pb">[000-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3120:3143'>賈誼新書説詩與魯詩合即騶虞可見矣劉歆曰詩始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3143:3166'>萌芽天下衆書往往頗出皆諸生雜説猶廣立於學宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3166:3181'>爲立博士在漢之儒惟賈生而已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3181:3204'>董仲舒春秋繁露及本集説棫樸雲漢及白牡騂剛諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3204:3223'>詩與毛詩不同是時三家早出蓋三家說也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3223:3243'>司馬遷曾向孔安國問故孔安國魯申公弟子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3243:3266'>劉向列女傳曾南豐譏其説詩多乖異不知向家世魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3266:3289'>詩也說苑新序亦然向子歆好春秋左傳及毛詩其與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3289:3316'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-10b' );" name="000-10b" class="pb">[000-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3316:3324'>毛異者皆魯詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3324:3347'>班固白虎通多引韓詩内傳亦時述魯詩漢書亦然蓋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3347:3355'>三家詩俱有之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3355:3375'>揚雄法言魯頌閟宫之說乖異大抵亦出三家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3375:3398'>蔡邕書魯詩石經其琴操亦多魯說唯獨斷載三頌之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3398:3418'>序俱同毛公朱氏經義考疑是魯序與毛同者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3418:3441'>鄭康成未箋毛傳時其注三禮多用魯詩兼出齊韓見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3441:3453'>鄭志答張逸及鄭駁異義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3453:3480'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-11a' );" name="000-11a" class="pb">[000-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3480:3499'>王肅崔靈恩皆毛詩家其注亦時出三家說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3519:3546'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-12a' );" name="000-12a" class="pb">[000-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3546:3552'>　　凡例</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3552:3575'>一三家詩魯最先出齊次之韓又次之故所録遺說以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3575:3593'>　魯齊韓爲次間有𥙷入則錯次録之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3593:3616'>一經文所標俱從毛詩不列其義但録三家遺說殘章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3616:3632'>　片語俱加輯録仍疏其得失於後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3632:3655'>一三家文字異者與經書子史所引古文竒字統爲一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3655:3678'>　卷列之於首以廣見聞其三家文字既異仍别有意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3678:3701'>　義者重録於各章各句之下書曰某作某然後可覽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3701:3728'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-12b' );" name="000-12b" class="pb">[000-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3728:3745'>　其說焉其文字異而義同者不重出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3745:3768'>一古逸詩或爲孔筆所删或删後之詩皆見經傳子史</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3768:3791'>　之引述三家如雨無正鼓鐘般諸篇句有逸出毛詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3791:3811'>　者皆當輯録故統爲一卷次於文字考異後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3811:3834'>一三家齊詩存者絶少魯訓故傳亦復無多唯韓詩亡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3834:3857'>　於北宋所存頗見一斑凡所輯録必注明出於何書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3857:3880'>一魯之孔安國劉向齊之匡衡翼奉韓之王吉諸人皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3880:3903'>　傳一家之學無所出入其董江都賈長沙班孟堅諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3903:3930'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-13a' );" name="000-13a" class="pb">[000-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3930:3953'>　説未知的出何家者則但標其名鄭司農少學韓詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3953:3976'>　兼通齊魯後乃箋毛今本所自言出於何家之說分</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3976:3982'>　别書之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3982:4004'>一韓詩外傳雖皆引詩証事亦時見本義間有節録</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4004:4027'>一三家訓故傳說遺文悉録原文不遺一字其他各家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4027:4042'>　所引述非有禆於經義者不録</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4042:4066'>一是編本王氏詩考更加蒐𥙷删正以成書掛漏錯失</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4066:4089'>　在所難免博雅之士聊以爲津筏可也其本論則具</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4089:4116'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '000-13b' );" name="000-13b" class="pb">[000-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4116:4124'>　載詩瀋中矣</span><br/>
